/PERSON>, a 37-year veteran of the group, told <ORGANIZATION> The </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Worcester </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Telegram </ORGANIZATION>. `` We had a fellow once who really had no musical ability, so we let him crash the cymbals.''
