Sunday's heavy police presence indicated the <LOCATION> Prague </LOCATION> leadership will not tolerate renewed protests against the invasion. The official Soviet news agency <ORGANIZATION> Tass </ORGANIZATION> reiterated Friday that the invasion was justified.
